{"tid":406773,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[問巴打]身材好正但無性欲 定係 身材一般但性欲強","createTime":"2017-09-20T02:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T03:29:11.000Z","uid":122028,"like":17,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c7d07e5552e8109259d06b708f9f54825828d85","tid":406773,"uid":122028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:34:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> -&gt; 樣又靚，又大波，有腰有蘿，又長腿又白滑。出街著咩衫都靚，總係會吸引好多男人目光。<br />\n但一個月~個零月先扑得一次野。又或者扑野果陣唔主動，叫佢含幾下又話攰，女上又話攰。總知好似好唔想扑野咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> -&gt; 身材一般。樣普普通通，對奶俾盡B cup左右，有個肚腩仔，條腿又唔算幼。著衫懶襯，咩衫都敢著出街，普通到好似啲人形紙板咁望都唔望。<br />\n但係床上面就chur住咁去。追撚住碌鳩黎含，唔俾佢含就眼濕濕想喊咁。咩體位都無問題，女上持久力勁到好似啲非洲長跑員咁。你射完之後仲會逗下袋，又奶下你碌鳩，引你再黎多Q。"},{"pid":"409c6d5ce6ea498f8a450ca35818077e8ca94614","tid":406773,"uid":2267,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/104006_ea6630fb331a6e3c9fdd69ad7b08fff0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F104006_ea6630fb331a6e3c9fdd69ad7b08fff0.jpg&h=63645740&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1647078ed86216f3b9b970e1e6f9dd62beeda8e","tid":406773,"uid":12179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:42:16.000Z","msg":"梗係要上面，再慢慢調教"},{"pid":"04ad92f64637aae2d2ce950cd8a63a27e9e40653","tid":406773,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T02:42:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/20/104006_ea6630fb331a6e3c9fdd69ad7b08fff0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F20%2F104006_ea6630fb331a6e3c9fdd69ad7b08fff0.jpg&h=63645740&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae0a7a7f8119b6dfd711